         <br/>
         Incoming students
         <i>
          not attending Orientation
         </i>
         <br/>
         Summer part-time students
        </td>
        <td style="padding: 0.25rem;">
         Fall Freshmen
         <br/>
         International students
         <br/>
         Transfer students
        </td>
       </tr>
      </tbody>
     </table>
     <br/>
     <h4>
      R'Card issuance requirements - please provide:
     </h4>
     <ol>
      <li>
       A valid government picture ID (see
       <a href="docs/accepted-proofs-of-identity.pdf" target="_blank">
        complete list
       </a>
       )
      </li>
      <li>
       Have been issued a student ID or
       <a href="https://ucpath.universityofcalifornia.edu/" target="_blank">
        employee ID number
       </a>
      </li>
      <li>
       Pay any fees for your R'Card. Accepted forms of payment includes: Visa, MasterCard,
                     or Discover. Sorry no cash accepted.
      </li>
      <ul style="padding-left:15px;">
       <li>
        Students are billed directly to their R'Web accounts
       </li>
       <li>
        Summer-only enrollment students pay a reduced $15 fee
       </li>
       <li>
        Employees and Affiliates pay at the time of service
       </li>
      </ul>
     </ol>
